# quantify-fluorescent-nucleus
A python package for segmentation of fluorescent nucleus, and measure the area of nucleus and the mean intensity per nucleus.

## Installation
Run the follwinf to install:
```python
pip install quantify-fluorescence-nucleus
```
## Usage

```python
from quantify_fluorescence_nucleus import ReferenceImage

# Load image and make ReferenceImage object


# Run smooting

# Run segmentation

# Extract data


```



